#String text
Display amount of cave dust fallen on tile when mining if you were present when it happened.\n\nHolding $b{$col[255,128,0]{SHIFT}} while activating this will turn on minesweeper cursor:\n• $col[255,128,0]{Clicking} with this cursor will add danger mark on the tile.\n• $col[255,128,0]{ALT+Clicking} will add safe mark to the tile.\n• $col[255,128,0]{CTRL+Clicking} will remove mark from the tile.
